===Yindidi===
Festac '77, he sọ yin yinyọnẹn di hùnwhẹ  ''Second World Black and African Festival of Arts and Culture'' tọn yin agọ́ nuwiwa akọ̀ tọn de yin bibasi to Surulere to [[Ayimatẹn Awọnlin Tọn|Awọnlin]], to [[Naijilia]],  bẹsọn azán 15tọ Alunlunsun 1977 tọn jẹ 12tọ Afínplọsun 1977 tọn. 
Finẹ wẹ bọlugbatẹn Awọnlin tọn Lagos National Stadium  (he sọgan hẹn gbẹtọ 60,000) he yin gbigbá to 1972 na Aihundida-Aflika tọn lẹpo lọ (the All-Africa Games) tin te. 

